Dialogue: 50,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.38,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu-Gomu no... Bazooka!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.14,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Retirem-se por enquanto, homens!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:58.14,0:02:01.14,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Todos! Encontrem qualquer saída que puderem!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Espere por nós! – Espere por nós!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Será que todos conseguimos?!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:09.32,0:02:12.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As pessoas com quem você estava quando saiu do navio estão aqui?! 
Dialogue: 50,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:16.62,0:02:17.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão Buggy não...
Dialogue: 50,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão Buggy não está aqui!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Finalmente terminei minha vistosa jangada!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:36.14,0:02:38.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parta!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que há com essa porcaria tão cedo?!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu me recuso a perder! Maldito!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou te comer!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Canhão Bara-Bara!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pare de lutar!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Apenas aceite seu destino!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpe! Desculpe!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:37.41,0:03:40.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Perdoe-me!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.63,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos! Vamos!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.76,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Meu plano é infalível!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Idiota! Idiota! Idiota!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu peguei ele!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fui{\i0} pego?! Ahn! O que?!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como as coisas acabaram assim?!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pare! Pare! Ai, ai, ai!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O fim já chegou?!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:24.20,0:04:24.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pare.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde estou agora?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saia deste lugar!{Gaimon 06:32}
Dialogue: 50,0:04:47.06,0:04:47.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem está aí?!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:48.56,0:04:51.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saia desta ilha imediatamente se você valoriza sua vida!{Gaimon 06:39 }
Dialogue: 50,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que são essas coisas?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Os ​​animais desta floresta.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não mexa com eles a menos que queira morrer!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:02.95,0:05:03.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:03.95,0:05:07.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses animais são bem chamativos e interessantes...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu disse para você não ir mais longe!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:12.63,0:05:13.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele atirou em mim! 
Dialogue: 50,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Errei!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aí está você!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:23.47,0:05:25.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Te peguei!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Saia!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.97,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Ai! Ai! Ai!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Você tem uma habilidade de fruta do diabo!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E daí se eu tiver?!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:32.85,0:05:33.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você não é nada...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que {\i1}é{\i0} você?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sua família valorizava muito você? 
Dialogue: 50,0:05:45.45,0:05:49.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim. Desde que eu era criança, eles expressavam seu amor por mim...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até parece!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa piada envelheceu rápido! 
Dialogue: 50,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja! Não seja arrogante!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:54.96,0:05:59.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não tenho piedade de quem mexe com esses animais!{Coelho}
Dialogue: 50,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah? Você quer lutar comigo?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:02.97,0:06:06.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu elogio sua bravura, mas não chore quando morrer! 
Dialogue: 50,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Te peguei!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Armas de longo alcance são trapaça!{Ravenfire/PJ}
Dialogue: 50,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E essa coisa aqui?! 
Dialogue: 50,0:06:27.66,0:06:29.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pare de ser egoísta!{Coelho}
Dialogue: 50,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Faça suas orações!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:46.68,0:06:49.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bara-Bara Fuga Rápida!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:51.35,0:06:57.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como você se atreve?! Exploda! Ai! 
Dialogue: 50,0:06:54.31,0:06:57.19,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Como ouso o quê?! Ahn?!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:06.91,0:07:10.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem mexe com os animais tem que pagar!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:10.83,0:07:15.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você veio a esta ilha para ir atrás dessas criaturas! 
Dialogue: 50,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que eu faria isso?!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nem {\i1}queria{\i0} vir aqui!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer que você não é um caçador furtivo?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você acha? Bom, né?!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É uma bebida que eu mesmo fiz!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, isso é o melhor!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me lembro da última vez que tomei uma bebida…
Dialogue: 50,0:07:45.49,0:07:49.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você pode ter quantas doses quiser! Beba!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E sinto muito pelo que aconteceu mais cedo! 
Dialogue: 50,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso foi uma coisa horrível que você fez,
Dialogue: 50,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas são águas passadas!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Saúde! – Saúde!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:09.51,0:08:13.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpe por pedir para você ajudar a fazer uma jangada também.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum. Foi um prazer.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:17.73,0:08:20.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ok! Cuide-se! 
Dialogue: 50,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você também!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Adeus, amigo!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tome cuidado!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 50,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você também!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zarpar!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.23,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Buggy...
Dialogue: 50,0:08:59.48,0:09:03.15,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Há muitas coisas estranhas nestas águas. 
Dialogue: 50,0:09:03.65,0:09:07.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Fique ainda mais seguro em sua jornada! 
Dialogue: 50,0:09:11.07,0:09:13.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espere, esqueci de contar a ele sobre isso!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Siga em frente, Buggy!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai! Saia daí!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.87,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Linda...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem é essa?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que gata!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:08.71,0:10:12.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bem, pelo menos ele parece estar salvo! 
Dialogue: 50,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele me fez suar muito aqui!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:19.52,0:10:26.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas de qualquer forma, cuide-se! 
Dialogue: 50,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigado pela ajuda!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu pensei que era um caso perdido lá!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não há necessidade de agradecimento.{Coelho}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é Buggy, o Palhaço, certo?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Como você sabe disso?!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:41.29,0:10:44.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou procurando um certo homem.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acredito que você o conheça?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele maldito pirralho de borracha!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja! 
Dialogue: 50,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Algum dia, acertarei as contas com você! 
Dialogue: 50,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Apenas espere!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse é o cara que você procura?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então é por isso que você me ajudou.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bem, o que você me diz? 
Dialogue: 50,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você se juntaria a mim?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Claro, por que não?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós dois temos o mesmo objetivo.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos trabalhar juntos.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:17.74,0:11:20.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é ótimo. Então, saúde!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Saúde!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:32.76,0:11:34.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão Buggy!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando ele estava vivo,\Nmuitas vezes eu sentia
Dialogue: 50,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,que ele era um capitão\Ncruel e assustador,
Dialogue: 50,0:11:42.68,0:11:48.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas agora percebo que ele era um pirata ousado e de coração aberto!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olhando para trás, podíamos saquear o quanto quiséssemos
Dialogue: 50,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,só porque tínhamos o apoio do Capitão Buggy! 
Dialogue: 50,0:11:55.19,0:12:01.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hoje, vamos realizar o maior e mais vistoso funeral do Capitão Buggy! 
Dialogue: 50,0:12:03.33,0:12:06.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão, descanse em paz!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor, deixe tudo comigo, Cabaji, o Acrobata, 
Dialogue: 50,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,primeiro imediato dos Piratas Buggy! 
Dialogue: 50,0:12:13.80,0:12:17.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Prometo reconstruir os Piratas Buggy!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cabaji!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.97,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:22.30,0:12:27.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É natural que o sucessor do Capitão Buggy seja eu,
Dialogue: 50,0:12:27.81,0:12:32.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,o primeiro imediato e incrível Domador de Bestas Mohji! 
Dialogue: 50,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu sou{\i0} o capitão!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos testar nossa força para ver quem será o capitão! 
Dialogue: 50,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem por mim!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(440,0)}– Mohji! Mohji! Mohji! – Mohji! Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Cabaji! Cabaji! Cabaji! – Cabaji! Cabaji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Mohji! Mohji! – Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Cabaji! Cabaji! – Cabaji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Mohji! Mohji! – Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Cabaji! Cabaji! – Cabaji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Mohji! Mohji! – Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:23.87,0:13:27.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que terei que lutar com você até seu corpo desmoronar!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, vamos brigar mano a mano.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou derrubar você com minhas próprias mãos!{Lor}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:45.39,0:13:50.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja... D-Desista já.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Não, você que deve desistir.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim! Nosso capitão Richie! - Sim! Nosso capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Nosso grande capitão! – Nosso grande capitão!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.42,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.67,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Nosso grande capitão! – Nosso grande capitão!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:59.67,0:15:00.42,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Nosso grande capitão! – Nosso grande capitão!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com o Capitão Buggy desaparecido,
Dialogue: 50,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,o mais digno de ser capitão é o capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Nosso grande capitão! – Nosso grande capitão!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Nosso grande Capitão! – Nosso grande Capitão!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Nosso grande capitão! – Nosso grande capitão
Dialogue: 50,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Nosso grande capitão! – Nosso grande capitão
Dialogue: 50,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie! – Capitão Richie! Capitão Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Nosso grande capitão! – Nosso grande capitão
Dialogue: 50,0:15:41.09,0:15:45.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você percebe que esta ilha pertence a nós, a Tribo Pata de Urso, certo?!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que divertido. Você quer brigar?! 
Dialogue: 50,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nós nos rendemos.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:22.84,0:16:24.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você encontrou algo bom?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim! Isso é...{Westfal}
Dialogue: 50,0:16:27.47,0:16:31.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,o navio pirata super chamativo dos Piratas Buggy!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas quem fez isso? Isso trás má sorte!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:36.93,0:16:40.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sem mencionar que este é um antigo pôster de procurado.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:40.94,0:16:43.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah? Tem alguém no chão ali.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê...?!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mohji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com vocês?!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:51.11,0:16:54.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Capitão Buggy...
Dialogue: 50,0:16:55.08,0:16:58.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É-É tão bom ver você.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou tão feliz que você esteja vivo! 
Dialogue: 50,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Achei que nunca mais veríamos você!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:04.92,0:17:07.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-eu também estou tão feliz!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:09.01,0:17:13.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas o que diabos aconteceu aqui? 
Dialogue: 50,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem fez isso com você?!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:17.27,0:17:20.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fomos socados do nada. 
Dialogue: 50,0:17:21.14,0:17:25.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É constrangedor, mas não conseguimos lembrar de nada. 
Dialogue: 50,0:17:25.82,0:17:29.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A tribo Pata de Urso fez isso.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se você vai salvá-los, é melhor se apressar.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:34.87,0:17:38.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os membros da tribo Pata de Urso são famosos por seu paladar exigente.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:51.68,0:17:55.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O capitão disse que os leões têm gosto ruim!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós também temos um gosto ruim!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não darei uma boa refeição de jeito nenhum! 
Dialogue: 50,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse cara parece melhor para comer do que eu! 
Dialogue: 50,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.44,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Mentira! Mentira!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele tem um gosto muito melhor!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:03.27,0:18:06.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou só ossos! Quase não tem carne em mim!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:08.78,0:18:10.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:10.28,0:18:13.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós somos a tribo Pata de Urso! Isso nos torna bons chefs!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um pouco de vinho e temperos vão tirar seu cheiro!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que fazemos com essa comida?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que são?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nunca vi ingredientes tão estranhos. 
Dialogue: 50,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos ferver isso com eles? 
Dialogue: 50,0:18:28.80,0:18:31.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Só espero que isso não perturbe meu estômago.{Ravenfire/Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:31.01,0:18:32.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bara-Bara-Bara...
Dialogue: 50,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bara-Bara-Bara-Bara...
Dialogue: 50,0:19:06.42,0:19:08.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é...?!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Remontar rapidamente!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:41.33,0:19:44.50,Main-207-,,0,0,8,,Estou de volta!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:45.37,0:19:49.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Capitão Buggy! – Capitão Buggy!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:51.42,0:19:54.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpe por ter demorado tanto, homens!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:55.42,0:19:59.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hora de animar as coisas com uma Buggy Ball super chamativa!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:18.95,0:20:22.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Acrobacias: Mistério de assassinato em fontes termais fumegantes!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:22.87,0:20:26.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que comece o show de domesticação de feras!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:33.25,0:20:37.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você realmente acha que pode acertar o grande Buggy, o Palhaço?! 
Dialogue: 50,0:20:39.97,0:20:42.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tenho que agradecer\Na todos vocês,
Dialogue: 50,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por tudo que fizeram aos meus\Nhomens!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lá vou eu chamativamente!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Chute Bara-Bara!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Soco Bara-Bara!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse é o nosso capitão!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:06.79,0:21:11.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Capitão Buggy! – Capitão Buggy!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou tão feliz que você esteja bem! 
Dialogue: 50,0:21:16.55,0:21:20.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu causei tanta dor a vocês, meus queridos subordinados! 
Dialogue: 50,0:21:21.01,0:21:24.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nossa dor não é nada!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:30.02,0:21:34.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todas as dificuldades que você teve foram por causa de... 
Dialogue: 50,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,aquele maldito Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:38.03,0:21:41.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A propósito, quem é essa adorável jovem? 
Dialogue: 50,0:21:42.36,0:21:46.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa linda mulher salvou minha vida! O nome dela é...
Dialogue: 50,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 50,0:21:48.37,0:21:50.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hum, me desculpe.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual era mesmo o seu nome?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:55.29,0:21:56.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todos!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:56.67,0:21:59.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os Piratas as Buggy estão de volta à ação!
Dialogue: 50,0:22:01.88,0:22:05.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão! O que devemos fazer primeiro? 
Dialogue: 50,0:22:05.51,0:22:09.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pegar a cabeça do Monkey D. Luffy!
